<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,1049,1365]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,1122,1148]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Comments:</emphasis>
<materialsCitation location="Here" municipality="The" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Rio Grande do Sul" typeStatus="lectotype">
This species is also polymorphic, even if this condition was not recognized among the individuals collected at ParNa Iguaçu. All the collected individuals were green, contrasting with the rust colour found both in the 
<typeStatus box="[194,297,1194,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">lectotype</typeStatus>
and in the individuals mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation author="Redtenbacher, J." box="[720,961,1194,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="315 - 562" refId="ref35573" refString="Redtenbacher, J. (1891) Monographie der Conocephaliden. Verhandelingen der Zoologisch- botanischen Gesellschaft Wien, 41, 315 - 562." type="journal article" year="1891">Redtenbacher (1891)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<collectingMunicipality box="[972,1016,1194,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">The</collectingMunicipality>
number of individuals of the species housed in the collections is uncertain, since this information was not presented in the original description, the same way that the number of specimens recorded for the 
<collectingRegion box="[723,993,1266,1292]" country="Brazil" name="Rio Grande do Sul" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Rio Grande do Sul State</collectingRegion>
was not reported in the aforementioned paper. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:D56DBD7DFFB8EF7BFF12FC1BFDF8FAEC:581B5AB0FFB8EF7BFF67FAA2FEADFA89" box="[226,280,1303,1329]" municipality="The" name="Here" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" stateProvince="Rio Grande do Sul">Here</location>
we present the first record of a male of this species
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,1049,1365]" box="[199,589,1338,1365]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,347,1338,1364]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Bioacoustics</emphasis>
